Package: CTEnrich
Type: Package
Title: Cell Type Enrichment Scoring and Visualization for Bulk RNA-seq
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Masaya", "Takasaki", role = c("aut", "cre"),
        email = "masaki03@uw.edu",
        comment = c(affiliation = "Department of Obstetrics and Gynecology, University of Washington")),
    person("Nobuhiko", "Hamazaki", role = "aut",
        comment = c(affiliation = "Department of Obstetrics and Gynecology, University of Washington")))
Description: Computes and visualizes cell type enrichment scores from bulk
    RNA-seq log2 fold-change results using cell-type marker gene sets.
    Supports per-condition dot plots, cross-condition comparisons, and
    AUC-based diversity curves.
URL: https://github.com/masayatakasaki/CTEnrich
BugReports: https://github.com/masayatakasaki/CTEnrich/issues
Imports:
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    ggplot2
